{
  "id": "6a04fbd4b8ea0ebb8c2ce188",
  "title": "あなたが思っているほど周りはあなたのことを気にしていない",
  "created": 1778711523,
  "updated": 1778715750,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a04fbd4b8ea0ebb8c2ce188",
      "text": "あなたが思っているほど周りはあなたのことを気にしていない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711523,
      "updated": 1778711523
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fbe2000000000017d781",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711523,
      "updated": 1778711523
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fbe3000000000017d782",
      "text": " [自意識過剰]な自分を調節するときに助かる概念",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711523,
      "updated": 1778711546
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fbfa000000000017d784",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711546,
      "updated": 1778711546
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fc69000000000017d78d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711658,
      "updated": 1778711658
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fc02000000000017d787",
      "text": "逆に、意外と見てる/見られている場合",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711555,
      "updated": 1778715750
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fc00000000000017d785",
      "text": " 推しのツイートを何度も見に行く",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711552,
      "updated": 1778711575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a050c590000000000a0c67c",
      "text": "  見に行きがち[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778715738,
      "updated": 1778715750
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fc02000000000017d786",
      "text": " ((自分の生産したブログやインターネット上の振る舞いをすべて見にくる人がいるということは想像しにくいけど、実際にある))",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711554,
      "updated": 1778711643
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fc49000000000017d78a",
      "text": "  井戸端で見た。後で探す",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778711626,
      "updated": 1778711630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04fc1e000000000017d788",
